    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141420/extras/6bf5a5ef243a502cc923458359a5e567.avif?t=1752223366\" width=610 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mirrormind is a 3D Puzzle Platformer in a unique lo-fi dithered style where you can shift perspective into any person you can see. Journey through a series of worlds where each world explores a shift in perspective. These shifts include an exploration of gravity, the 2nd person perspective, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141420/extras/dd231e97a75019fda5d607f50eacbde0.poster.avif?t=1752223366\" width=610 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141420/extras/dd231e97a75019fda5d607f50eacbde0.webm?t=1752223366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141420/extras/dd231e97a75019fda5d607f50eacbde0.mp4?t=1752223366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141420/extras/fd50137b753f14c5bf0bc3b94efedacf.avif?t=1752223366\" width=610 height=110 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 4 visually striking worlds about switching perspectives: using different directions of gravity, controlling yourself in the 2nd person perspective and switching between past and present.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 different puzzles, each focused on showing some unique and interesting consequence of its mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique undo system where you can reverse time to quickly explore other solutions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A parallel and optional narrative exploring themes of perspective, senses, sights and experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire Challenge Collectables which unlock Appendix levels, unique levels experimental levels that highlight other decision decisions.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mirrormind treats your time as precious; there is no filler in this game and the levels have been crafted to minimise tedium and frustration. There are no puzzles that require a high degree of dexterity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141420/extras/8873e5ca78fb3705a8c593230394207a.avif?t=1752223366\" width=610 height=130 /></span></p>",
